reviewText: These guys are more fun than... should be legal!! ;-)  Super players!

I found this group accidentally on you tube, looking for brass quintets.  The caught my attention with their talent, and kept it with the off-the-wall humor.  My kids enjoyed this, asking to bring it to school, etc.
You will enjoy, and be sure to share with others.  I wish these guys traveled the states, I'd love to see them live!
The musicianship and entertainment displayed on this DVD cannot be done justice with words. If you have seen this group on youtube you know what they can do. This DVD is one of their better ones.
